TELL THEM, DES.

00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,543
MY SISTER
SAVED UP HER MONEY

00:09:03,543 --> 00:09:05,678
TO GIVE ME
A GORGEOUS CASHMERE SWEATER.

00:09:05,678 --> 00:09:08,948
I LOVED IT, I TREASURED IT,
AND THEN...

00:09:08,948 --> 00:09:09,616
I SHRUNK IT.

00:09:09,616 --> 00:09:12,519
WITH THE HELP OF CHEMISTRY,
WE'VE DEVELOPED A REVOLUTIONARY

00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:14,521
NEW PRODUCT
